                <Commands>
                  <Command>
                    <Text>          
  
Create Member 
  CurrentCube.[Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Quarter to Date] 
  As "NA";   
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PY Multifamily Permits]
 AS Sum(
{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
[Measures].[Multifamily Permits]
), 
FORMAT_STRING = "0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'MSA Permits Metro'  ;   
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PY Total Permits]
 AS Sum(
{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
[Measures].[Total Permits]
), 
FORMAT_STRING = "0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'MSA Permits Metro'  ;   
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PYT3M Total Permits]
 AS Sum(
{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
[Measures].[Total Permits]
), 
FORMAT_STRING = "0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'MSA Permits Metro'  ;

 AS [Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[Single-family Permits], 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales'  ;   
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Total Permits Change]
 AS IIF( Sum(
			{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
			[Measures].[Total Permits]
			) = 0, 0,  


 (
              Sum(
		    		{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(2):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember},
		    		[Measures].[Total Permits]
				  ) 
                    -
              Sum(
			        {[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
			        [Measures].[Total Permits]
			      )
            )
                /
            (
               Sum(
	        		{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
	        		[Measures].[Total Permits]
	        		)
            )

), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.00%;-#,##0.00%", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'MSA Permits Metro'  ;   
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Perform Indicator]
 AS IIF( Sum(
			{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
			[Measures].[Sales]
			
			) = 0, 0,  


 (
              Sum(
		    		{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(2):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember},
		    		[Measures].[Sales]
				  ) 
                    -
              Sum(
			        {[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
			        [Measures].[Sales]
			      )
            )
                /
            (
               Sum(
	        		{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
	        		[Measures].[Sales]
	        		)
            )

)
-
IIF( Sum(
			{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
			[Measures].[Single-family Permits]
			) = 0, 0,  


 (
              Sum(
		    		{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(2):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember},
		    		[Measures].[Single-family Permits]
				  ) 
                    -
              Sum(
			        {[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
			        [Measures].[Single-family Permits]
			      )
            )
                /
            (
               Sum(
	        		{[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(14):[Time].[Month].CurrentMember.Lag(12)},
	        		[Measures].[Single-family Permits]
	        		)
            )

), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.00%;-#,##0.00%", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'MSA Permits Metro'  ;

 AS [Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[Multifamily Permits],

Create Member 
  CurrentCube.[Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Year to Date] 
  As "NA";                     
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PScore]
 AS Iif([Measures].[P Score Sales]=0,NULL,[Measures].[Weighted P Score Sales]/[Measures].[P Score Sales]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.000;-#,##0.000", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                    
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PScoreNew]
 AS Iif([Measures].[P Score Sales]=0,
NULL,([Measures].[PScore]-0.500)*[Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[P Score Sales]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.000;-#,##0.000", 
VISIBLE = 0 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                              
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Invoices #]
 AS [Measures].[Fact Sales N Ivoices Count], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                    
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PScore Contribution]
 AS Iif([Measures].[P Score Sales]=NULL or [PScore]= NULL,
NULL,([Measures].[PScore]-0.500)*[Measures].[Sales]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                               
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Bookings Margin $ ]
 AS [Measures].[Bookings]-[Measures].[Bookings Cost], 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Bookings';             
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[AvgPrice]
 AS [Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[Shipped Qty], 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';     
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Sales - Canadian Dollars - Estimated]
 AS [Measures].[Sales]*1.33, 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                            
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Invoices Count]
 AS [Measures].[Invoice Num Distinct Count], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                            
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Orders Count]
 AS [Measures].[Order Num Distinct Count], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                            
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Customers Count]
 AS [Measures].[Cust Num Distinct Count], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                            
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Products Count]
 AS [Measures].[Prod Num Distinct Count], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0;-#,##0", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';              
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Goal % Complete]
 AS [Measures].[PTD Goal]/[Measures].[Goal], 
FORMAT_STRING = "Percent", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Inside Sales Goal';                                       
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Budget % Complete]
 AS [Measures].[PTD Budget]/[Measures].[Budget], 
FORMAT_STRING = "Percent", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Budget';                               
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Bookings GP%]
 AS ([Measures].[Bookings]-[Measures].[Bookings Cost])/[Measures].[Bookings], 
FORMAT_STRING = "#,##0.00 %;-#,##0.00 %", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Bookings';                                       
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PTD Budget % Achieved]
 AS IIF([Measures].[PTD Budget]=0, NULL, [Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[PTD Budget]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "Currency", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Budget';              
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[PTD Goal % Achieved]
 AS IIF([Measures].[PTD Goal]=0, NULL, [Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[PTD Goal]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "Percent", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Inside Sales Goal';            
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Budgeted Avg Daily Sales]
 AS IIF([Measures].[Budget]=0, NULL, [Measures].[Budget]/[Measures].[Days]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Budget';                                      
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Budget % Achieved]
 AS IIf([Measures].[Budget]=0,0,[Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[Budget]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "Percent", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Budget';                                      
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Days % Complete]
 AS [Measures].[PTD Days]/[Measures].[Days], 
FORMAT_STRING = "Percent", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Days';              
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Goal % Achieved]
 AS IIf([Measures].[Goal]=0,0,[Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[Goal]), 
FORMAT_STRING = "Percent", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Inside Sales Goal';                                       
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Daily Sales Rate ]
 AS [Measures].[Sales]/[Measures].[PTD Days], 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Sales';                         
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Daily Bookings Rate]
 AS [Measures].[Bookings]/[Measures].[PTD Days], 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Bookings';                                       
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Daily Sales Required ]
 AS IIf(([Measures].[Days]-[Measures].[PTD Days])=0,0,([Measures].[Budget]-[Measures].[Sales])/([Measures].[Days]-[Measures].[PTD Days])), 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Budget';              
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Goal Daily Sales Required ]
 AS IIf(([Measures].[Days]-[Measures].[PTD Days])=0,0,([Measures].[Goal]-[Measures].[Sales])/([Measures].[Days]-[Measures].[PTD Days])), 
FORMAT_STRING = "$#,##0.00;($#,##0.00)", 
VISIBLE = 1 ,  ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP = 'Fact Inside Sales Goal';                                                                
  
Create Member 
  CurrentCube.[Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Month to Date] 
  As "NA";                                                  

// Year to Date
  (
    [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Year to Date],
    [Time].[Year].[Year].Members,
	[Time].[Date].Members 
  ) 
  
  =

  Aggregate(
             { [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Current Time] } 
             *
             PeriodsToDate(
                            [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date].[Year],
                            [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date].CurrentMember
             )
  );                                       



 

Scope(
       {
         [Measures].[Shipped Qty],
         [Measures].[Sales],
         [Measures].[Gross Margin]
       }
);                                                                

  
// Quarter to Date
  ( 
	[Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Quarter to Date],
    [Time].[Quarter].[Quarter].Members,
	[Time].[Date].Members 
  ) 
  
  =

  Aggregate(
             { [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Current Time] } 
             *
             PeriodsToDate(
                            [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date].[Quarter],
                            [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date].CurrentMember
             )
  );                                                                

  
// Month to Date
  ( 
	[Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Month to Date],
    [Time].[Month].[Month].Members,
	[Time].[Date].Members 
  ) 
  
  =

  Aggregate(
             { [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date Time Calculations].[Current Time] } 
             *
             PeriodsToDate(
                            [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date].[Month],
                            [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date].CurrentMember
             )
  );                                                                

  
End Scope;                                     

                         

Scope ([Measures].[Gross Margin Perc]);                               
    THIS = [Measures].[Gross Margin]/[Measures].[Sales];                                
     FORMAT_STRING(THIS)="#,##0.00 %;-#,##0.00 %";                               
End Scope;                                 
/*
  End Time Intelligence script for the [Time].[Year -  Quarter -  Month -  Date] hierarchy.
*/

/*
The CALCULATE command controls the aggregation of leaf cells in the cube.
If the CALCULATE command is deleted or modified, the data within the cube is affected.
You should edit this command only if you manually specify how the cube is aggregated.
*/
CALCULATE; </Text>
                  </Command>
                </Commands>
              </MdxScript>
            </MdxScripts>
            <Kpis>
              <Kpi>
                <ID>KPI</ID>
                <Name>Budget</Name>
                <AssociatedMeasureGroupID>Fact Business Days</AssociatedMeasureGroupID>
                <Value>[Measures].[PTD Budget % Achieved]</Value>
                <Goal>1
</Goal>
                <Status>CASE
WHEN [Measures].[PTD Budget % Achieved]&gt;=1 THEN 1
WHEN [Measures].[PTD Budget % Achieved]&gt;=0.95 AND [Measures].[PTD Budget % Achieved]&lt; 1 THEN 0
WHEN [Measures].[PTD Budget % Achieved]&lt;0.95  THEN  -1
END
</Status>
                <TrendGraphic>Standard Arrow</TrendGraphic>
                <StatusGraphic>Traffic Light</StatusGraphic>
              </Kpi>
            </Kpis>
            <ErrorConfiguration>
              <KeyErrorLimit>-1</KeyErrorLimit>
              <KeyErrorLimitAction>StopLogging</KeyErrorLimitAction>
              <KeyNotFound>IgnoreError</KeyNotFound>
              <NullKeyNotAllowed>IgnoreError</NullKeyNotAllowed>
            </ErrorConfiguration>

              <SilenceInterval>-PT1S</SilenceInterval>
              <Latency>-PT1S</Latency>

                      <xs:element name="dbo_FactSales" msprop:IsLogical="True" msprop:FriendlyName="FactSales" msprop:DbTableName="FactSalesTableALL" msprop:TableType="View" msprop:QueryDefinition="SELECT        FSAD.CompanyID, FSAD.ProdNum, FSAD.CustNum, FSAD.InvoiceDate, FSAD.ShippingWhseNum, FSAD.ShippedQty, FSAD.ExtNetprice / FSAD.CurrencyRate AS ExtNetprice, &#xD;&#xA;                         FSAD.ExtAccountingCost / FSAD.CurrencyRate AS ExtAccountingCost, FSAD.ExtGM / FSAD.CurrencyRate AS ExtGM, FSAD.ProdWhse, FSAD.ShipViaCode, FSAD.SalesRep1, FSAD.OrderSource, FSAD.InvoiceDateMonthsBack, &#xD;&#xA;                         FSAD.InvoiceDateQuartersBack, FSAD.InvoiceDateYearsBack, FSAD.ExtCommCost / FSAD.CurrencyRate AS ExtCommCost, FSAD.InvoiceNum, FSAD.MerchandiseAmt / FSAD.CurrencyRate AS MerchandiseAmt, &#xD;&#xA;                         FSAD.ExtGMCommCos / FSAD.CurrencyRate AS ExtGMCommCos, FSAD.ShipToSlsmn, FSAD.DayOfMonth, FSAD.GPP, FSAD.CurrencyCode, FSAD.PromoCode, FSAD.WrittenBy, FSAD.SellingPriceVariance, FSAD.OrderNum, &#xD;&#xA;                         FSAD.OrderEntryDate, CheckSum(FSAD.OrderNum) AS OrderNum2, FSAD.PriceRange, &#xD;&#xA;                         CASE WHEN PriceRange = 'Above Start' THEN '1' WHEN PriceRange = 'Near Start' THEN '2' WHEN PriceRange = 'Around Target' THEN '3' WHEN PriceRange = 'Near Floor' THEN '4' WHEN PriceRange = 'Below Floor' THEN '5' ELSE&#xD;&#xA;                          '6' END + FSAD.PriceRange AS OrderPriceRange, CASE WHEN PriceRange NOT IN ('Promo', 'Capital Equipment', 'No Advice') THEN ExtNetPrice ELSE 0 END AS PScoreSales, &#xD;&#xA;                         CASE WHEN PriceRange = 'Above Start' THEN 1.0 WHEN PriceRange = 'Near Start' THEN 0.75 WHEN PriceRange = 'Around Target' THEN 0.50 WHEN PriceRange = 'Near Floor' THEN 0.25 WHEN PriceRange = 'Below Floor' THEN&#xD;&#xA;                          0.0 ELSE 0.0 END * FSAD.ExtNetprice AS WeightedPScoreSales, ISNULL(FSAD.PriceSourceCode, 'Unknown') AS PriceSourceCode, ISNULL(price.OrderHistoryLinePriceType.PriceType, 'Unknown') AS PriceType, &#xD;&#xA;                         ISNULL(price.OrderHistoryLinePriceType.PriceType, 'Unknown') + ISNULL(FSAD.PriceSourceCode, 'Unknown') AS PriceTypeCode, FSAD.OrderType, FSAD.PercentCredit&#xD;&#xA;FROM            FactSalesTableALL AS FSAD WITH (nolock) LEFT OUTER JOIN&#xD;&#xA;                         price.OrderHistoryLinePriceType WITH (nolock) ON FSAD.OrderNumAll = price.OrderHistoryLinePriceType.OrderNum AND FSAD.CompanyID = price.OrderHistoryLinePriceType.CompanyID AND &#xD;&#xA;                         FSAD.LineNumber = price.OrderHistoryLinePriceType.LineNumber" msprop:QueryBuilder="SpecificQueryBuilder">
